dct_title_s: Netherlands, Rotterdam Waterway and the Maas : Hoek van Holland to Rotterdam
dct_description_sm: Depths shown by isolines and soundings. "Universal transverse mercator (UTM) grid. Zone 31U, International spheroid for military grid references". "Soundings in meters."
